Class GenericsMath

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.swisscheese.swisscheese.math.GenericsMath

  • public class GenericsMath
extends java.lang.Object
    A method to do mathematical calculations on variables of generic type.

    Operations currently supported:

  • Addition
  • Subtraction
  • Multiplication
  • Casting
